{"tid":1457823,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家有冇諗過p牌有一日會過","createTime":"2019-08-12T12:20:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T16:36:36.000Z","uid":130981,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"711252cc5050c6b18549f6bf1fe6363a232d2425","tid":1457823,"uid":130981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:20:25.000Z","msg":"鬼ac遲早會成為連登一部分<br />\n連仔已經為大家做左好多 亦承受左好多風險<br />\n唔可以依賴連仔解決一切問題<br />\n我地要真正長遠咁解決個問題<br />\n唯一嘅方法就係習慣獨立思考<br />\n隨波逐流人云亦云已經證明左遲早會中伏好易比人帶風向<br />\n要唔比人帶風向 就要習慣去思考見到嘅嘢<br />\n唔好再迷信多正評就一定啱<br />\n要習慣fact check 左先<br />\n唔好夠juicy 就正評就信<br />\n否則你只會成為被帶風向嘅一分子<br />\n希望大家可以習慣思考 停一停諗要諗<br />\n唔好比別有用心嘅人利用<br />\n越危急越要冷靜思考<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不分化不割𥱊不篤灰</span></span>"},{"pid":"b93b202d760f9e5842f6b52f5f304983e3a7620c","tid":1457823,"uid":130981,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:21:24.000Z","msg":"p一世咩<br />\n遲早都會完p<br />\n到時如果未贏 個情況一樣會出現"},{"pid":"86fd704bda233343f85d352637a3ecaae09aae31","tid":1457823,"uid":182574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:21:59.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"6a4457389b111d0d3c5c50c714065bad04c932b2","tid":1457823,"uid":130981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:22:04.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"202bf04534b90482f090afa20f61d2ad0a4cf6c0","tid":1457823,"uid":124133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:23:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a8c8c24b019b3ca3278651939b3aea50e363b6c","tid":1457823,"uid":130981,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:23:46.000Z","msg":"民主係雙刃劍<br />\n如果成班都係唔用腦嘅愚民<br />\n民主唔會解決到任何問題<br />\n要多數人都有知識有邏輯思考 <br />\n民主先會真正有效"},{"pid":"478ab8ad9791de6c17573a8bdad7bbe5ef0bf823","tid":1457823,"uid":265197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:23:59.000Z","msg":"係<img s